# Image Gallery

This project was developed as part of my internship at CodeAlpha.

## Description
The Image Gallery is a responsive web application that displays a collection of images in an organized and visually appealing layout. It allows users to view images in a structured grid and adapts to different screen sizes for a smooth viewing experience across devices.

## Technologies Used
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

## Learning Outcomes
Through this project, I gained practical experience in:
- Creating responsive layouts using CSS
- Structuring web pages with semantic HTML
- Implementing interactive behavior with JavaScript
- Designing user-friendly image gallery interfaces

